License-file:        LICENSE
Author:              Kevin Quick
Maintainer:          Kevin Quick <quick@sparq.org>
Build-Type:          Simple
Cabal-Version:       >=1.2
Category:            Text
Stability:           Unstable


Library
  Build-Depends:     base >= 4 && < 5
  Exposed-modules:   Text.Format.Para
  ghc-options:       -Wall
